cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.MA 

The paper is about reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The use of potential-based reward shaping and ensembles also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The application of these techniques to improve learning speed in robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY) is also mentioned. Finally, the use of an ensemble of policies is a common technique in multi-agent systems (cs.MA).
